					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>I look forward to 2080 when someone is writing a piece on the SCOFLDOP HyperWiki dunking on the author of this article.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/planet-jane" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5407607&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569398968" alt="planet Jane" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5407607)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/planet-jane" >planet Jane</a></span>, this sort of personally directed comment is unhelpful and unnecessary. Critique the writing, not the writer.</p> 
