					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10360962#post-4374533</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10360962/scp-3846#post-4374533</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2019 16:06:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>planet Jane</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5407607</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>there's something deeply ironic about these comments.</p> <p>This article is uninteresting and is just a vehicle for an opinion that I can't imagine most of the people who've upvoted this actually share&#8212;when is the last time you had a strong opinion on Thoreau?</p> <p>I don't even like Thoreau, this is just insufferably smug.</p> <p>-1</p> <p>I look forward to 2080 when someone is writing a piece on the SCOFLDOP HyperWiki dunking on the author of this article.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
