					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10360962#post-4159735</guid>
				<title>This Author Commentary is Thoreauly Uninteresting.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10360962/scp-3846#post-4159735</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 20 Feb 2019 21:16:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ihp</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1267048</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is probably the shortest SCP I've written in a long while. It came based off of me re-reading an article in the New Yorker called &quot;Pond Scum&quot;, which pretty much tore into Thoreau's life and in the process, <em>Walden</em>. I hadn't read <em>Walden</em> in over seven years, and when I first read it, I remembered hating it viscerally. Now that I've re-read it for the sake of this skip, I can confirm that it is bad, but in the boring sense not in the sense of &quot;I want to fucking dig up Thoreau and feed his remains into a furnace&quot;.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550702592" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/literallymechanical" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2829014&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550702592" alt="LiterallyMechanical" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2829014)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/literallymechanical" >LiterallyMechanical</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notexactlyhuman" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3143506&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1550702592" alt="Notexactlyhuman" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3143506)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notexactlyhuman" >Notexactlyhuman</a></span> for Beta-reading this. Enjoy!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
